        description: "Apply seasonal variation to the environment via MaterialParameterCollection. Creates/updates MPC_Season with parameters that materials can reference: SeasonPhase (0-1 mapping spring→summer→autumn→winter), LeafColorShift (tint overlay), GrassDensityScale (reduces in winter), SnowCoverage, BranchBareness. Materials wired to MPC_Season will react instantly. Pairs with create_pbr_material and create_foliage_material_preset for full seasonal support.",
