        description: "Generate a complete building mesh from a 2D floor-plan polyline. Extrudes walls with configurable thickness and height, auto-generates floor and ceiling slabs, and optionally cuts window and door openings via boolean subtraction. Saves the result as a Nanite-ready UStaticMesh asset and spawns it in the level. Input is a JSON array of [x,y] wall vertices (world XY), plus opening definitions.",
