        description: "Scatter canopy trees across a landscape using UE5's instanced foliage system. Accepts one or more foliage-ready static mesh paths, places them with spacing and slope filtering, and saves generated foliage type assets so the level remains stable across editor restarts. Skeletal mesh inputs are rejected because per-tree SkeletalMeshActor placement is unstable for saved forest maps.",
