        description: "Ecology-aware tree placement using Poisson disk sampling with ecological rules. Reads landscape heightmap to compute slope, elevation, and moisture zones. Detects water bodies and places moisture-loving species nearby. Places conifers at higher elevations and on north-facing slopes. Places deciduous trees in valleys and moderate slopes. Enforces minimum spacing via Poisson disk rejection. Complements simulate_ecosystem (which paints layers) by actually placing tree instances.",
