        description: "Configure replication properties on an actor using standard AActor APIs. Works without Iris. Set any combination of: replicates, replicate_movement, dormancy, net_update_frequency, min_net_update_frequency, net_cull_distance, net_priority, always_relevant, only_relevant_to_owner, net_load_on_client, use_owner_relevancy. Only supplied parameters are modified; omitted parameters are left unchanged.",
